WEBVTT

00:00.901 --> 00:02.334
<i>- previously on warehouse 13...</i>

00:02.400 --> 00:03.701
- whoever stole the sword

00:03.767 --> 00:05.801
Has other things that
belong in the warehouse,

00:05.868 --> 00:08.467
Which would mean
that we have competition.

00:08.534 --> 00:10.534
- lattimer and bering,
right?

00:10.601 --> 00:15.367
They're so raw, so untrained,
so corruptible.

00:15.434 --> 00:17.100
- what about your folks?

00:17.167 --> 00:18.534
- colorado springs.

00:18.601 --> 00:22.300
They own a bookstore
called bering & sons.

00:22.367 --> 00:24.501
- well, he must be proud
of you.

00:24.567 --> 00:27.033
<i>- you ever see that movie,
the great santini,</i>

00:27.100 --> 00:31.667
With the tough dad
and the scared kids?

00:31.734 --> 00:33.667
- it's like that, huh?

00:33.734 --> 00:36.601
- yeah, except it wasn't over
in two hours.

